block content
  p Hi #{name}!!
  p Sometimes you just want to send a simple HTML email with a simple design and clear call to action. This is it.
  table.btn.btn-primary(role="presentation", border="0", cellpadding="0", cellspacing="0")
    tbody
      tr
        td(align="left")
          table(role="presentation", border="0", cellpadding="0", cellspacing="0")
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}`, target="_blank") Call To Action
  p I hope you will find password reset link in this letter.
  p Good luck!

  //- href=`${url}` - той url, який ми передаємо в конфігу emailService